I am not sure if it is a good check that is called here. You don't delete data, you modify metadata. In io.prestosql.sql.analyzer.StatementAnalyzer.Visitor#visitAnalyze we check privilege for insert which is also weird.
I think we should have dedicated method for modifying statistics.
@electrum Any thoughts?

